#: base/models/settings.py:71
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"we hope you’re happy with eventyay as your event’s CfP system.\n"
"These links may be helpful in the coming days and weeks:\n"
"\n"
"- Your event’s dashboard: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- A list of proposals: {event_submissions}\n"
"- Your schedule editor: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"नमस्कार,\n"
"\n"
"इव्हेंटचा CfP सिस्टम म्हणून eventyay वापरताना समाधान वाटत असेल अशी आशा आहे.\n"
"पुढील काही दिवस आणि आठवड्यांत या लिंक्स उपयोगी ठरू शकतात:\n"
"\n"
"- इव्हेंटचा डॅशबोर्ड: {event_dashboard}\n"
"- प्रस्तावांची यादी: {event_submissions}\n"
"- शेड्यूल संपादक: {event_schedule}\n"
"\n"
"काहीही कमी वाटत असल्यास, कृपया eventyay.com वरील वेबसाइटद्वारे संपर्क साधा.\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:90
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"just writing you to let you know that your Call for Participation is now\n"
"closed. Here is a list of links that should be useful in the next days:\n"
"\n"
"- You’ll find a list of all your {submission_count} proposals here:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- You can add reviewers here:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- You can review proposals here:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- And create your schedule here, once you have accepted proposals:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"
msgstr ""
"नमस्कार,\n"
"\n"
"कळवण्यासाठी लिहित आहोत की Call for Participation आता\n"
"बंद झाली आहे. पुढील काही दिवसांत उपयुक्त ठरतील अशा लिंकची यादी:\n"
"\n"
"- सर्व {submission_count} प्रस्तावांची यादी येथे उपलब्ध आहे:\n"
"  {event_submissions}\n"
"- पुनरावलोकक येथे जोडता येतील:\n"
"  {event_team}\n"
"- प्रस्तावांचे पुनरावलोकन येथे करता येईल:\n"
"  {event_review}\n"
"- प्रस्ताव स्वीकारल्यानंतर, शेड्यूल येथे तयार करता येईल:\n"
"  {event_schedule}\n"

#: base/models/settings.py:112
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Hi,\n"
"\n"
"congratulations, your event is over! Hopefully it went well. Here are some\n"
"statistics you might find interesting:\n"
"\n"
"- You had {submission_count} proposals,\n"
"- Of which you selected {talk_count} sessions.\n"
"- The reviewers wrote {review_count} reviews.\n"
"- You released {schedule_count} schedules in total.\n"
"- Over the course of the event, you sent {mail_count} mails.\n"
"\n"
"If there is anything you’re missing, please contact us via our website on "
"eventyay.com.\n"
msgstr ""
"नमस्कार,\n"
"\n"
"अभिनंदन, तुमचा कार्यक्रम संपला आहे! आशा आहे की तो छान पार पडला. येथे काही\n"
"आकडेवारी दिली आहे जी कदाचित उपयुक्त वाटेल:\n"
"\n"
"- एकूण {submission_count} प्रस्ताव होते,\n"
"- त्यापैकी {talk_count} सत्रे निवडली,\n"
"- परीक्षकांनी {review_count} पुनरावलोकने लिहिली,\n"
"- एकूण {schedule_count} वेळापत्रके प्रकाशित केली,\n"
"- कार्यक्रमादरम्यान {mail_count} ईमेल पाठवले.\n"
"\n"
"काही गोष्टींची कमतरता वाटत असल्यास, eventyay.com वरील आमच्या वेबसाइटद्वारे संपर्क "
"साधा.\n"

