#: submission/forms/submission.py:37
msgid "Additional Speaker"
msgstr "अतिरिक्त वक्ता"

#: submission/forms/submission.py:39
msgid ""
"If you have a co-speaker, please add their email address here, and we will "
"invite them to create an account. If you have more than one co-speaker, you "
"can add more speakers after finishing the proposal process."
msgstr ""
"सह-वक्ता असल्यास, कृपया येथे त्यांचा ईमेल पत्ता जोडा; त्यांना खाते तयार करण्यासाठी आमंत्रण "
"पाठवले जाईल. एकापेक्षा जास्त सह-वक्ते असल्यास, प्रस्ताव प्रक्रिया पूर्ण केल्यानंतर अधिक वक्ते "
"जोडता येतील."

#: submission/forms/submission.py:152
msgid "Select a session type"
msgstr "सत्र प्रकार निवडा"

#: submission/forms/submission.py:172
msgid ""
"Please contact the organizers if you want to change how often you’re "
"presenting this proposal."
msgstr ""
"हा प्रस्ताव किती वेळा सादर करायचा आहे ते बदलायचे असल्यास, कृपया आयोजकांशी संपर्क साधा."

